name: Phonerental

overview: Phonerental provides temporary mobile communications by renting international cell phones, satellite phones, blackberries and GPS equipment to corporations and individuals. Focused on customer satisfaction and providing the most adequate service for each client, the company will go to great lengths to simplify the complex world of mobile communications. Founded in Argentina in 2001, it currently has offices in Argentina, Mexico and the United States. As part of its global network it has strategic partners in France, Japan, Spain and the United Kingdom. Cell phone rental solutions for the US, UK, France, Italy, Japan and South Korea to name a few of a long list of customized answers to travelers communication needs.
